rget\" class=\"w-5 h-5 text-orange-400\" data-kid=\"133\"></i>\n              </div>\n              <p class=\"text-[15px] text-slate-300 leading-relaxed font-medium\" data-kid=\"134\">Optimize <span class=\"text-white font-bold\" data-kid=\"135\">space complexity</span> in your algorithm — currently O(n), target O(1) for large datasets.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"flex gap-5 p-5 rounded-2xl bg-orange-500/5 border border-orange-500/10 group hover:bg-orange-500/15 transition-all duration-300\" data-kid=\"136\">\n              <div class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-orange-500/20 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0\" data-kid=\"137\">\n                <i data-lucide=\"zap-off\" class=\"w-5 h-5 text-orange-400\" data-kid=\"138\"></i>\n              </div>\n              <p class=\"text-[15px] text-slate-300 leading-relaxed font-medium\" data-kid=\"139\">Refine behavioral responses: Reduce usage of <span class=\"text-white font-bold\" data-kid=\"140\">filler words</span> ('um', 'like') by ~30% for cleaner delivery.</p>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      \n      <div class=\"lg:col-span-5 glass-card p-10 flex flex-col animate-in self-stretch h-full\" style=\"animation-delay: 0.9s\" data-kid=\"141\">\n        <div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 mb-10\" data-kid=\"142\">\n          <div class=\"p-3.5 rounded-2xl bg-violet-600/20 border border-violet-500/30 shadow-xl shadow-violet-900/20\" data-kid=\"143\">\n            <i data-lucide=\"graduation-cap\" class=\"w-7 h-7 text-violet-400\" data-kid=\"144\"></i>\n          </div>\n          <div data-kid=\"145\">\n            <h3 class=\"font-bold text-white text-2xl font-heading leading-tight tracking-tight\" data-kid=\"146\">Learning Roadmap</h3>\n            <p class=\"text-[11px] text-violet-400 font-black uppercase tracking-[0.25em] mt-1\" data-kid=\"147\">AI-Powered Curriculum</p>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"space-y-12 flex-1 relative mt-4\" data-kid=\"148\">\n          \n          <div class=\"absolute left-[15px] top-4 bottom-4 w-0.5 bg-gradient-to-b from-violet-500/50 via-slate-800 to-transparent\" data-kid=\"149\"></div>\n          \n          \n          <div class=\"pl-14 relative group\" data-kid=\"150\">\n            <div class=\"absolute left-0 top-1.5 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-violet-600 border-[6px] border-[#111128] flex items-center justify-center shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(139,92,246,0.4)] group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform\" data-kid=\"151\"></div>\n            <div class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-center justify-between gap-2 mb-3\" data-kid=\"152\">\n              <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-white font-heading tracking-tight\" data-kid=\"153\">Mastering System Design</h4>\n              <span class=\"text-[10px] font-black text-violet-300 bg-violet-500/20 border border-violet-500/30 px-3 py-1 rounded-full w-fit\" data-kid=\"154\">IN PROGRESS</span>\n            </div>\n            <p class=\"text-[14px] text-slate-400 mb-5 leading-relaxed font-medium\" data-kid=\"155\">Focus on distributed caching strategies and database sharding for planetary-scale apps.</p>\n            <div class=\"flex items-center gap-5\" data-kid=\"156\">\n              <div class=\"flex-1 h-2 bg-white/5 rounded-full overflow-hidden border border-white/5\" data-kid=\"157\">\n                <div class=\"h-full bg-gradient-to-r from-violet-600 to-indigo-500 rounded-full\" style=\"width: 45%\" data-kid=\"158\"></div>\n              </div>\n              <span class=\"text-xs font-black text-slate-500 w-10\" data-kid=\"159\">45%</span>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n\n          \n          <div class=\"pl-14 relative opacity-80 group\" data-kid=\"160\">\n            <div class=\"absolute left-0 top-1.5 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-slate-700 border-[6px] border-[#111128] group-hover:bg-slate-600 transition-colors\" data-kid=\"161\"></div>\n            <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-white font-heading mb-2 tracking-tight\" data-kid=\"162\">Advanced React Architecture</h4>\n            <p class=\"text-[14px] text-slate-400 mb-5 leading-relaxed font-medium\" data-kid=\"163\">Deep dive into Compound Components and Render Props for high-performance libraries.</p>\n            <div class=\"flex items-center gap-5\" data-kid=\"164\">\n              <div class=\"flex-1 h-2 bg-white/5 rounded-full overflow-hidden border border-white/5\" data-kid=\"165\">\n                <div class=\"h-full bg-slate-600 rounded-full\" style=\"width: 10%\" data-kid=\"166\"></div>\n              </div>\n              <span class=\"text-xs font-black text-slate-500 w-10\" data-kid=\"167\">10%</span>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n\n          \n          <div class=\"pl-14 relative opacity-50 group\" data-kid=\"168\">\n            <div class=\"absolute left-0 top-1.5 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-slate-800 border-[6px] border-[#111128]\" data-kid=\"169\"></div>\n            <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-white font-heading mb-2 tracking-tight\" data-kid=\"170\">Leadership & Executive Presence</h4>\n            <p class=\"text-[14px] text-slate-400 leading-relaxed font-medium\" data-kid=\"171\">Practice the STAR-E method for senior leadership and conflict resolution scenarios.</p>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <button class=\"neon-button mt-14 py-5 px-8 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center gap-4 text-lg font-black shadow-2xl transition-all hover:gap-6 active:scale-[0.98]\" data-kid=\"172\">\n          Explore Full Roadmap <i data-lucide=\"arrow-right\" class=\"w-6 h-6\" data-kid=\"173\"></i>\n        </button>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    \n    <footer class=\"pt-8 border-t border-white/5 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-4 animate-in\" style=\"animation-delay: 1s\" data-kid=\"174\">\n      <p class=\"text-xs font-bold text-slate-600 uppercase tracking-[0.3em]\" data-kid=\"175\">AI Interview Feedback Engine v2.4.0</p>\n      <div class=\"flex items-center gap-6\" data-kid=\"176\">\n        <a href=\"#\" class=\"text-xs font-bold text-slate-500 hover:text-white transition-colors\" data-kid=\"177\">Privacy Policy</a>\n        <a href=\"#\" class=\"text-xs font-bold text-slate-500 hover:text-white transition-colors\" data-kid=\"178\">Terms of Service</a>\n        <a href=\"#\" class=\"text-xs font-bold text-slate-500 hover:text-white transition-colors text-right flex items-center gap-2\" data-kid=\"179\">\n          Contact Support <i data-lucide=\"external-link\" class=\"w-3 h-3\" data-kid=\"180\"></i>\n        </a>\n      </div>\n    </footer>\n  </div>\n\n  <script data-kid=\"181\">\n    document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {\n      // Initialize Lucide icons\n      lucide.createIcons();\n\n      // Radar Chart\n      const radarOptions = {\n        series: [{\n          name: 'Score',\n          data: [82, 88, 74, 90, 85, 78],\n        }],\n        chart: {\n          height: 350,\n          type: 'radar',\n          offsetY: 10,\n          toolbar: { show: false },\n          background: 'transparent',\n          dropShadow: {\n            enabled: true,\n            blur: 10,\n            left: 1,\n            top: 1,\n            opacity: 0.1\n          }\n        },\n        colors: ['#8b5cf6'],\n        stroke: { width: 2 },\n        fill: { opacity: 0.2 },\n        markers: { size: 4, colors: ['#8b5cf6'], strokeWidth: 2 },\n        xaxis: {\n          categories: ['Technical', 'Communication', 'Confidence', 'Fluency', 'HR Readiness', 'Problem Solving'],\n          labels: {\n            show: true,\n            style: {\n              colors: Array(6).fill('#94a3b8'),\n              fontSize: '12px',\n              fontWeight: 600,\n              fontFamily: 'Inter, sans-serif'\n            }\n          }\n        },\n        yaxis: {\n          show: false,\n          min: 0,\n          max: 100\n        },\n        grid: {\n          show: true,\n          borderColor: 'rgba(255,255,255,0.05)',\n        },\n        theme: { mode: 'dark' }\n      };\n\n      const radarChart = new ApexCharts(document.querySelector(\"#radar-chart\"), radarOptions);\n      radarChart.render();\n\n      // Timeline Area Chart\n      const timelineOptions = {\n        series: [{\n          name: 'Your Score',\n          data: [85, 72, 88, 81, 92, 89]\n        }, {\n          name: 'Avg. Benchmark',\n          data: [75, 78, 80, 76, 82, 79]\n        }],\n        chart: {\n          height: 300,\n          type: 'area',\n          toolbar: { show: false },\n          background: 'transparent',\n          zoom: { enabled: false },\n          sparkline: { enabled: false }\n        },\n        colors: ['#8b5cf6', 'rgba(255,255,255,0.1)'],\n        dataLabels: { enabled: false },\n        stroke: { curve: 'smooth', width: [3, 2], dashArray: [0, 5] },\n        fill: {\n          type: 'gradient',\n          gradient: {\n            shadeIntensity: 1,\n            opacityFrom: 0.45,\n            opacityTo: 0.05,\n            stops: [20, 100, 100, 100]\n          }\n        },\n        grid: {\n          borderColor: 'rgba(255,255,255,0.03)',\n          strokeDashArray: 4,\n          padding: { left: 0, right: 0 }\n        },\n        xaxis: {\n          categories: ['Intro', 'Technical Q1', 'Technical Q2', 'Coding', 'Behavioral', 'Closing'],\n          axisBorder: { show: false },\n          axisTicks: { show: false },\n          labels: {\n            style: { colors: '#475569', fontSize: '10px', fontWeight: 600 }\n          }\n        },\n        yaxis: {\n          min: 0,\n          max: 100,\n          tickAmount: 4,\n          labels: {\n            style: { colors: '#475569', fontSize: '10px', fontWeight: 600 }\n          }\n        },\n        tooltip: {\n          theme: 'dark',\n          x: { show: true },\n          y: { formatter: (val) => val + '%' }\n        },\n        legend: { show: false }\n      };\n\n      const timelineChart = new ApexCharts(document.querySelector(\"#timeline-chart\"), timelineOptions);\n      timelineChart.render();\n    });\n  </script>\n</div>\n",
